        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Retry",
        "Completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把六个参与者和主流程画出来了：Aggregate→Event Store→Reactor→Queue→Queue Worker→Side Effect。现在加上alt分支，成功路径是Side Effect返回Success，Worker标记Job为Completed；失败路径返回Failure，Worker触发Retry。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
